Step 1: Choose Your Focus and Target Audience
Considerations:

Target Audience: Choose one that is easy to relate to. Given that simplicity and quick understanding are key, middle or secondary school students might be the best fit‚Äîthey're curious and engaged with science, but also open to playing imaginative games.
Game Setting: Decide on a setting that will resonate with your audience. For instance:
